Package de.cau.cs.kieler.sim.kiem.config.properties

This package contains the data storing classes for the configuration manager and the schedule manager.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ConfigDataComponent Holds all information needed for the currently running schedule.
For example:
Aimed Step Duration
Timeouts
...and user defined variables
EditorDefinition Definition class for the editor.
Contains the name of the editor and an editor id.
KiemConfigEvent Slightly modified version of the original KiemEvent.
MostRecentList<T> This implements a collection that can update according to most recent use.
New items will be added at index 0 and all items already in
it will be pushed down.
ScheduleData Holds all data needed to manage a specific schedule.
